  "title": "Human Resource cum Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>You will support the Human Resource Manager with daily HR tasks including processing leave applications, managing payroll, coordinating onboarding, and handling ad-hoc duties such as assisting with IR8A, IR21 forms, client invoices, vehicle matters, and childcare leave. You will apply your knowledge of MOM rules and regulations to ensure compliance.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Process leave applications accurately to support employee attendance tracking</li><li>Manage payroll tasks to ensure timely and correct salary disbursement</li><li>Coordinate onboarding activities to facilitate smooth new hire integration</li><li>Assist with preparing IR8A and IR21 tax forms to comply with regulatory requirements</li><li>Handle client invoice processing to support financial operations</li><li>Manage vehicle-related administrative matters to maintain company assets</li><li>Support childcare leave administration in line with company policies and MOM regulations</li><li>Apply knowledge of MOM rules and regulations to ensure HR compliance</li><li>Perform ad-hoc HR and administrative duties as assigned to support team needs</li></ul><p><strong>Preferred competencies and qualifications</strong></p><ul><li>Prior experience in human resources or administrative roles</li><li>Strong organizational skills demonstrated by managing multiple HR tasks efficiently</li><li>Effective communication skills to liaise with employees and external parties</li><li>Proficiency in MS Office and HR information systems to perform daily HR functions</li></ul>",
